    • generatePerson

      public Person generatePerson(String username, String gender, int generations, int birthYear, boolean root) throws DaoException
      Generates a person and their ancestors with semi-random information
      Parameters:
      username - Username to fill data for
      gender - Gender of the person
      generations - Number of generations left to fail
      birthYear - Birth year of person
      root - Boolean, true if the person is the root and won't have a death date
      Returns:
      Person p which is the user base object
      Throws:
      DaoException - if there is an error with the DAOs
